## Discussion

When the [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARFrame/worldMappingStatus-swift.property] of the session’s [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARSession/currentFrame] is [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARFrame/WorldMappingStatus-swift.enum/notAvailable], the session has no internal map of the real-world space around the device, nor the scene visible to the camera. Calling [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARSession/getCurrentWorldMap(completionHandler:)] at this time results in an error.

This status occurs shortly after starting a new session. To save or share a world map, wait for the user to explore their surroundings and the session’s status to change to [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARFrame/WorldMappingStatus-swift.enum/mapped] or [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARFrame/WorldMappingStatus-swift.enum/extending].

# ARFrame.WorldMappingStatus.notAvailable

**Case**

No world map is available.

## Declaration

```swift
case notAvailable
```

## Discussion

When the [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARFrame/worldMappingStatus-swift.property] of the session’s [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARSession/currentFrame] is [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARFrame/WorldMappingStatus-swift.enum/notAvailable], the session has no internal map of the real-world space around the device, nor the scene visible to the camera. Calling [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARSession/getCurrentWorldMap(completionHandler:)] at this time results in an error.

This status occurs shortly after starting a new session. To save or share a world map, wait for the user to explore their surroundings and the session’s status to change to [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARFrame/WorldMappingStatus-swift.enum/mapped] or [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARFrame/WorldMappingStatus-swift.enum/extending].
